collections.name: Shuffled Atlas
collections.description:
Cards on the table—where, and when, do you play your hand? 'Shuffled Atlas' deals out 160 unique one-of-one works, each placing the timeless drama of card playing into a different setting, era, and style. From the breezy palm trees of 'Club Miami' to the flickering torchlight of the 'Gilded Goblet,' each NFT shuffles history, geography, and artistic tradition into a hand unlike any other. But player beware! Some NFTs are more rare than others! 

This Orangehare In-House Production shuffles the deck on artistic creation, mixing original paintings by Chae Tongyull and Orangehare designers with AI-assisted design and curated model sets. With distinct traits and styles ranging from medieval tapestries to pop art prints, 'Shuffled Atlas' proves that no matter the time, place, or fortune, the game—and the gamble—remains the same. So—where would you play your hand?"

collections.name: Neon Canverse A Pop Art Rebellion
collections.description:
Welcome to Neon Canverse, where the raw energy of street art collides with the bold commercialism of pop culture. Inspired by Andy Warhol’s fascination with everyday objects, this collection transforms ordinary soda cans into electrifying works of neon art, dripping in vibrant hues of electric blue, magenta, orange, and gold.

Each can tells a story—drenched in abstract neon textures, reflecting the chaotic beauty of consumerism, nostalgia, and the underground art scene. The backdrop bursts with dripping paint, a nod to graffiti culture and the unpredictability of artistic expression.

This collection is for those who see art in the mundane, rebellion in the ordinary, and beauty in the bold. Own a piece of Neon Canverse, and let the revolution of color ignite your collection. 🚀🌈

collections.name: NATURE'S GOLD
collections.description: Preserving nature is of paramount importance, not only for its intrinsic and unsurmountable beauty but also for its indispensable contributions to human life. The natural world offers a wondrous tapestry of diverse ecosystems that inspire awe and reverence, serving as a source of artistic and spiritual inspiration. Beyond beauty, nature provides essential services, such as clean air, fresh water, fertile soil, and a stable climate, which are crucial for our survival and well-being. By rescuing and safeguarding these precious natural environments, we protect the biodiversity that sustains our agricultural systems and medical innovations and ensure that future generations can enjoy and benefit from the Earth’s natural bounty. Therefore, committing to conservation and sustainable practices is not merely an act of stewardship, but a vital investment in humanity's future. This collection is my attempt to capture the drama and beauty of this, God's greatest gift.

collections.name: Bunny Suzy
collections.description:
Her gaze is languid and sly, sparkling with mischief and promise, as if inviting her into a game where she sets the rules. Her lips, sensual and full, are parted in a slight half-smile, like a frozen kiss.

And, of course, rabbit ears. Despite their innocent nature, they are here a symbol of freedom and audacity. They sway to the beat of her movements, twitching playfully, then freezing in anticipation. These little pranks add playfulness and provocation to the image, emphasizing her sexuality, but not vulgar, but rather graceful and confident.

collections.name: Cute kitty Alice
collections.description:
Her beauty is a gentle charm woven from graceful lines and soft colors. She's like a painting come to life, with pastel shades of hair framing a porcelain-like face. Her eyes are like azure lakes, full of fun and mischief, or maybe deep thoughtfulness. Her lips, like a rosebud, are slightly parted in a gentle smile, revealing snow-white teeth.

The character of this girl is modest, because her friends did not really like her for her sincere beauty and mocked her out of envy.
Alice misses those friends who protected her and did not understand why the world was so unfair to her. Nevertheless, she has not lost
the positive in the depths of her soul and still hopes to meet a loved one who will love her as much as she does.
